50|$|Between 2003-2015, <b>The</b> <b>Believer</b> was {{published}} by McSweeney’s, the independent press founded in 1998 by Dave Eggers. Eggers designed <b>The</b> <b>Believer’s</b> original design template. Park left <b>The</b> <b>Believer</b> in 2011, with Julavits and Vida continuing to serve as editors. In 2017, the magazine found a new home, moving from McSweeney's to the Beverly Rogers, Carol C. Harter Black Mountain Institute, an international literary center at the University of Nevada, Las Vegas. <b>The</b> <b>Believer</b> is currently edited by Joshua Wolf Shenk.|$|R
